23:25.660 --> 23:31.340
He says you can't even have the faintest trace of probability with regard to the future.

23:31.980 --> 23:38.140
Every occurrence is a brand new event. All events are loose and separate.

23:38.140 --> 23:42.380
There is no necessity about any conjunction of events.

23:42.940 --> 23:48.460
