29:29.580 --> 29:35.820
contingent truths? You say certainly not. Those are laws and principles of reality. Say no such

29:35.820 --> 29:43.820
category. It's either a subjective relation of ideas, or it is a brute contingent sensualist

29:43.820 --> 29:49.500
type fact. Therefore, as far as metaphysics is concerned, throw it into the fire.

29:52.300 --> 29:57.500
